OOC: I had thought it was a ship that crashed into a mountain, and was thus 
mostly buried.  In any case it should be hard to penetrate.

::Aerotaur::
       He looks worried.  "You know what happened to the last bot he 
reprogrammed.  And I like you just the way you are.  But if you're set on 
doing this I'll support you all the way."  He half grins.
